
Completion conditions:

first M
first M within time T
first M within time T that meet condition C 
first M within time T that meet condition C before exception E

first M that meet condition C 
first M that meet condition C before exception E

first M before exception E



join limit 5, timeout 3m, condition($quote.amount < 100)

join timeout 3m, condition($quote.amount < 100)





